description:
Conan and Kogoro are taken to a warehouse by the gang of thieves to wait for their boss Mr. Head. Suddenly Head`s metallic altered voice comes over the speakers. Kogoro looks at his watch and panics when he sees the time is 2:30 in the morning. If he doesn`t determine who killed Head`s son by dawn, Ran will be killed by an assassin.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: あやつられた名探偵 (後編)
